high_descs: Turn to the left, pick up the toilet paper tube
Turn around, walk to the bath tub
Put the toilet paper tube on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Take the toilet paper tube off the floor, put it on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around to the left and find the toilet plunger.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the floor.
Take the roll and move to the right so that you're facing the other side of the toilet.
Place the roll on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Pick up an empty toilet paper roll and place it on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk slightly forward to the toilet paper holder.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the floor.
Turn around and walk to the other side of the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the top of the toilet, to the left of the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move an empty roll of toilet paper from the floor to the top of a toilet.
